         </xi:fallback>\n             </xi:include>\n\t  <xi:include href=\"../alists/charDecl.xml\">\n\t     <xi:fallback>\n\t       <p>ISicily glyphs authority list</p>\n\t     </xi:fallback>\n\t   </xi:include>\n         </encodingDesc>\n        <profileDesc>\n            <calendarDesc>\n                <calendar xml:id=\"julian\">\n                    <p>Julian Calendar</p>\n                </calendar>\n            </calendarDesc>\n            <langUsage>\n                <language ident=\"en\">English</language>\n                <language ident=\"it\">Italian</language>\n                <language ident=\"grc\">Ancient Greek</language>\n                <language ident=\"la\">Latin</language>\n                <language ident=\"he\">Hebrew</language>\n                <language ident=\"phn\">Phoenician</language>\n                <language ident=\"xpu\">Punic</language>\n                <language ident=\"osc\">Oscan</language>\n                <language ident=\"xly\">Elymian</language>\n                <language ident=\"scx\">Sikel</language>\n                <language ident=\"sxc\">Sikan</language>\n            </langUsage>\n            <textClass>\n                <keywords scheme=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins.html\">\n                    <term ana=\"#function.building\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins/lod/86.html\">building</term>\n                </keywords>\n            </textClass>\n        </profileDesc>\n        <revisionDesc status=\"edited\">\n            <listChange>\n                <change when=\"2016-12-03\" who=\"#JCu\">James Cummings autogenerated EpiDoc output from database</change>\n                <change when=\"2019-07-09\" who=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag revised the file on the basis of work for 2017 edition</change>\n                <change when=\"2020-09-09\" who=\"#system\">Updated Zenodo DOI</change>\n            \t   <change when=\"2020-10-05\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova normalised Unicode</change>\n            \t   <change when=\"2020-10-08\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova updated list of languages</change>\n            \t\t<change when=\"2020-11-26\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova restructured bibliography</change>\n\t    <change when=\"2020-12-18\" who=\"#system\">Updated Zenodo DOI</change>\n            \t<change when=\"2021-01-19\" who=\"#SS\">renumbered files, uris and references</change>\n\t</listChange>\n        </revisionDesc>\n    </teiHeader>\n    <facsimile>\n        <surface type=\"antiquarianEdition\">\n            <graphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic003037_tiled.tif\" height=\"516px\" width=\"1444px\">\n                <desc>Detail of Agustín transcription from Prestianni 1987, p.302</desc>\n            </graphic>\n            <graphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic003037.jpg\" height=\"516px\" width=\"1444px\">\n                <desc>Detail of Agustín transcription from Prestianni 1987, p.302</desc>\n            </graphic>\n        </surface>\n    </facsimile>\n    <text>\n        <body>\n            <div type=\"edition\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"grc\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                <ab>\n                    <lb n=\"1\"/><hi rend=\"stacked\">Τω</hi>βίας · <roleName type=\"paracivic.religious\" subtype=\"episkopos\"><expan><abbr>ἐπίσ</abbr><ex>κοπος</ex></expan></roleName>\n                    <lb n=\"2\"/>ἔκτισεν\n                </ab>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"apparatus\">\n                <listApp><app><note>Text after Prestianni</note></app>\n                    <app loc=\"Line 1\"><note>Τ is directly above ω in the transcription</note></app></listApp>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                <p>Bishop Tobias founded (this)</p>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"commentary\">\n                <p>The text is one of six that Antonio Agustín recorded as having seen in the church of S. Maria dei Palazzi on the site of Halaesa. Unlike the other five, it was not subsequently recorded by later visitors to the site (cf. e.g. Gualtherus 1624) and has not been seen or recorded since until the edition of Prestianni Giallombardo (1987). There is good reason to believe that Agustín recorded the letter forms accurately, and if so these provide some grounds for a date: the letter forms are comparable to those in the funerary inscription of Eirena (late fourth or fifth century AD) and Prestianni Giallombardo notes Syracusan parallels from the first third of the fifth century AD (1987: 303 n.24). However a substantially later date is also possible, and Prestianni Giallombardo notes firstly that the name Tobias is rare in Sicily, and likely to indicate an immigrant from the eastern Mediterranean, and secondly that there is limited evidence for a bishopric at Halaesa from the seventh century onwards. On this basis she plausibly suggests that Tobias was bishop at Halaesa in the course of the seventh century AD, and the inscription therefore records his construction of a building of some description on the site.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"bibliography\">\n                <listBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    <bibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"SEG\">\n                        <citedRange>41.0776</citedRange>\n                        <ptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F2GG87EQ\"/>\n                    <ref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</ref></bibl>\n                    <bibl>\n                        <author>Prestianni Giallombardo</author>\n                        <date>1988-1989</date>\n                        <citedRange>363-365 dr</citedRange>\n                        <ptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/RJ839CID\"/>\n                    <ref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001662\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001662</ref></bibl>\n                    <bibl>\n                        <author>Prestianni Giallombardo</author>\n                        <date>1987</date>\n                        <ptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/29XU2HR9\"/>\n                    <ref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001663\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001663</ref></bibl>\n                    <bibl>\n                        <author>Facella</author>\n                        <date>2006</date>\n                        <citedRange>306-307</citedRange>\n                        <ptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/J4XWZPV6\"/>\n                    <ref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002013\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002013</ref></bibl>\n                    <bibl>\n                        <author>Prag and Tigano</author>\n                        <date>2017</date>\n                        <citedRange>no.49</citedRange>\n                        <ptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/MI64NB9L\"/>\n                    <ref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002630\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002630</ref></bibl>\n                </listBibl>\n\t   <listBibl type=\"discussion\"><bibl/></listBibl>\n            </div>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>\n",
